{"tid":2147549,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"狼隊違反公平財政條例 被罰2屆歐戰球員名單由25人減至23人","createTime":"2020-08-09T10:23:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-13T04:27:25.000Z","uid":35562,"like":37,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"07fa2665fbf5277cbf9b4a946b707d7ab24a5e55","tid":2147549,"uid":35562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T10:23:34.000Z","msg":"繼曼城之後，狼隊都被歐洲足協控告違反公平財政條例，不過呢支英超新勢力判罪比較輕，僅被罰未來2屆歐洲賽減少註冊球員人數，「A名單球員」由原本25人減至23人。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">歐洲足協指狼隊今季虧蝕3000萬歐元</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，未能達到財政平衡要求，被罰未來2屆歐洲賽減少註冊球員人數，以及罰款20萬歐元，如果下季再未能降解決赤字，將加大罰款至60萬歐元。相比之前曼城被判罰禁止參加2屆歐洲賽，明顯輕好多，估計狼隊唔會提出上訴。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，狼隊一直依賴同一班主力征戰各條戰線，減少註冊2位球員，影響有限。同埋狼隊今季英超只排第7位，已經無緣參加下屆歐霸盃，如果佢喺想出戰下屆歐洲賽，唯一方法係奪得今屆歐霸盃，出戰下屆歐聯。<br />\n<br />\nffp真係弱鳩智<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"888b9bfdaec2a07c51220767fd19ff177af03c38","tid":2147549,"uid":191926,"like":39,"dislike":0,"score":39,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T10:30:27.000Z","msg":"psg同曼城  <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfebbf6e38066d185e59ee51d6ad02b9afda1a6c","tid":2147549,"uid":84081,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T10:31:29.000Z","msg":"Ffp喺武肺下都照樣罰狼隊真係on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3000萬咪蝕喺門票收入同人工支出"},{"pid":"ed17d6ed603834c53ab23db0411ce056083e5d76","tid":2147549,"uid":136099,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"quote":{"pid":"888b9bfdaec2a07c51220767fd19ff177af03c38","tid":2147549,"uid":191926,"like":39,"dislike":0,"score":39,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T10:30:27.000Z","msg":"psg同曼城  <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T10:31:49.000Z","msg":"窮人含撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9706aa0184daad015ab03a6dd0a3e207d43e2f7d","tid":2147549,"uid":240975,"like":1